headline: Jim Cramer on Expedia: “It’s Much Cheaper Than Key Competitor”
summary: Expedia Group, Inc. (NASDAQ:EXPE) is one of the relatively cheap S&P 500 stocks Jim Cramer talked about. Cramer noted that the stock is cheaper than its main competitor.
